reviews.comment: Thank you Shaeel, he helped guide and assisted in getting the Webpage designed and uploaded to the new Server.  Make sure that whoever you choose to design a website will assist with this step.  Couldn't of done it without his help!

This was a very poor project that was never finalized or delivered.   We were waiting for revisions, and now the order was marked as completed.  Nothing was completed as requested and the site was not what we discussed.  We even sent mock-ups of how we wanted it to look, and yet nothing was even close (including the basic tab names of the site).  We want to cancel the order, and would have never marked it as completed.  Unfortunately, the order status can not be changed once it is marked as complete.  Therefore no way to request a refund.  This is a complete scam, and now has cost us over $1,000 and a lot of time wasted.

seller_response.comment: The mock up were ready and i am waiting for you guys to reply you guys are unresponsive since December mid if you check the inbox you will see my message where i have tried to contact you soo many times. If you guys are available now I am still open to work. Thanks.

reviews.comment: I was excepting less but its fine, next time we will talk in detail first

The experience was overall good, Shaeel was pretty easy to communicate with and was effective at completing the tasks in hand. There were some issues at first but within a day they were fully addressed and there was a very satisfactory result. Would recommend

Shaeel Rajpoot was a fantastic website developer! The professionalism and quality of his work exceeded my expectations—completely bug-free result. He was cooperative, fluent in language, and always willing to make updates and assist as needed. Well done, Shaeel! 🙌
